snippet: Dempsey scored his first international hat trick in the Americans’ 6-0 victory in a Gold Cup quarterfinal, drawing praise from his teammates and coach for his attitude.
abstract: American forward Clint Dempsey scores his first international hat trick in United States men's team's 6-0 victory over Cuba in Gold Cup soccer tournament quarterfinals.
